Extraversion.Low: You are introverted and may prefer quieter settings and need alone time to recharge.
Extraversion.Medium: You are somewhat extraverted and enjoy socializing, but also need some alone time.
Extraversion.High: You enjoy socializing and may feel energizedby being around others.

Agreeableness.Low: You are not agreeable and may be competitive and even manipulative.
Agreeableness.Medium: You are somewhat agreeable, but some of the time you are selfless and some selfish.
Agreeableness.High: You are agreeable and have a great deal of interest in other people.

Conscientiousness.Low: You are not very conscientious and may procrastinate important tasks and be unorganized.
Conscientiousness.Medium: You are somewhat conscientious and may be organized in some aspects of life but not in others.
Conscientiousness.High: You are conscientious, you pay attention to detail and are very organized with a set schedule.

Neuroticism.Low: You are not very neurotic and tend to be relaxed and deal well with stress.
Neuroticism.Medium: You are somewhat neurotica and can handle your emotions well most of the time
Neuroticism.High: You are neurotic and tend to worry about many things as well as get upset easily.

Openness.Low: You are not very open to experience and tend to dislike change or new ideas.
Openness.Medium: You are somewhat open to experience and like to try new things some of the time.
Openness.High: You are open to experience, always trying new things and very adventurous.
